data.title: Don't tax the rich
data.description:
"Don't Tax the Rich" T-Shirt

 

Are you tired of your hard-earned millions being nibbled away by pesky taxes? Say no more! Our "Don't Tax the Rich" tee is here to make your financial woes fashionable.

Product Features:

- Heavy cotton construction (as weighty as your financial portfolio)

- Slogan strategically placed above the heart (where your money is)

- Durable print (lasts longer than most tax loopholes)

- Available in a color that pairs well with gold bars

Perfect for:

- Casual Fridays at the hedge fund

- Your next audit appointment (the heavy fabric helps you stand your ground)

- Yacht parties (doubles as a sail in strong winds)

 

Our heavy cotton tee is built to last, much like the wealth gap it references. It's so durable, it might outlast your tax avoidance schemes!

Remember, wearing this shirt doesn't actually exempt you from taxes. But hey, it's cheaper than hiring a team of accountants to find loopholes!

Disclaimer: Embezzle Ensemble does not condone tax evasion. We just dress for it.ű

data.title: Tax Fraud Is Hot
data.description:
"Tax Fraud is Hot" Hoodie

Who says financial crimes can't be cozy? Wrap yourself in the warm embrace of our "Tax Fraud is Hot" hoodie – perfect for those chilly nights when you're cooking the books!

Why You'll Love It:

- Softer than your smoothest tax evasion scheme
- Warm enough to keep you toasty during those long nights of "creative accounting"
- Spacious kangaroo pocket (ideal for stashing offshore account statements)
- Hood deep enough to hide from the IRS (just kidding, they always find you)
- Drawstrings color-matched to the base (because attention to detail is key in both fashion and fraud)

Perfect for:

- Casual Fridays at your shell company
- Cozy nights in with your favorite audit paperwork
- Beach walks while discussing "business opportunities" with potential investors
- Lounging around your living room, planning your next big "financial maneuver"

Our "Tax Fraud is Hot" hoodie is so comfortable, you might forget you're wearing it – much like how you "forgot" about that offshore account. Oops!

Remember, while tax fraud may be hot, it's also illegal. This hoodie is for entertainment purposes only. We recommend pairing it with a strong moral compass and a good accountant.

Disclaimer: Embezzle Ensemble does not condone tax fraud or any other financial crimes. We just dress for the scandal, not the sentence!
